SELECT 
--Datum AS Datum,
sum(Sachsen) AS Sachsen, 
sum(SachsenAnhalt) AS SachsenAnhalt, 
sum(Thueringen) AS Thueringen, 
sum(Regionales) AS Regionales, 
sum(Inland_mit_Regionalbezug) AS Inland_mit_Regionalbezug, 
sum(Inland_Welt) AS Inland_Welt, 
sum(Gesamt) AS Gesamt, 
sum(Audio) AS Audio, 
sum(Video_1x1) AS Video_1x1, 
sum(Video_16x9) AS Video_16x9,
EXTRACT(MONTH FROM Datum) AS Monat

from `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.MDR.AppAktuell_ContentType_external`
WHERE EXTRACT(MONTH FROM Datum) = $month_as_number 
AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM Datum) = $Jahr
GROUP BY Monat
--GROUP BY mo

SELECT 
Datum AS Datum,
Sachsen, SachsenAnhalt, Thueringen, Regionales, Inland_mit_Regionalbezug, Inland_Welt, Gesamt, Audio, Video_1x1, Video_16x9

from `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.MDR.AppAktuell_ContentType_external`
WHERE EXTRACT(MONTH FROM Datum) = $month_as_number 
AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM Datum) = $Jahr

query.rawSql:
WITH all_months AS(
  SELECT "Januar" as monat, 1 as monat_num
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "Februar", 2
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "März", 3
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "April", 4
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "Mai", 5
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "Juni", 6
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "Juli", 7
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "August", 8
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "September", 9
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "Oktober", 10
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "November", 11
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "Dezember", 12
--  UNION ALL
--  SELECT "Jahr", 13
)
SELECT monat FROM all_months
WHERE 
CASE  
  WHEN $Jahr = 2022 THEN monat NOT IN ("Januar","Februar","März","April","Mai", "Juni")
--WHEN $Jahr = 2024 AND CURRENT_DATE > "2024-09-07" THEN monat NOT IN ("September", "Oktober", "November", "Dezember", "Jahr")
  ELSE 1=1 --NOT IN ("August","September", "Oktober", "November", "Dezember", "Jahr") 
END

SELECT CAST(number AS STRING) FROM (
SELECT
CASE "$Monat"
WHEN "Januar" THEN 1
WHEN "Februar" THEN 2
WHEN "März" THEN 3
WHEN "April" THEN 4
WHEN "Mai" THEN 5
WHEN "Juni" THEN 6
WHEN "Juli" THEN 7
WHEN "August" THEN 8
WHEN "September" THEN 9
WHEN "Oktober" THEN 10
WHEN "November" THEN 11
WHEN "Dezember" THEN 12
END as number)
